{"slug":"incarnation-of-money","title":{"en":"Incarnation of Money","km":"អំណាចទឹកប្រាក់"},"description":{"en":"A drama based on law about money, love and passion. It is about lobbying, rebating, connecting and corruption of the Korean society through Lee Cha Don, who loses everything because of money.\n\nLee Cha Don is a man who rises to the seat of a special branch prosecutor with the money of a loan shark, while Bok Jae In is the daughter of the loan shark who raised Lee Cha Don.","km":"រឿងភាគដែលផ្អែកលើច្បាប់អំពីលុយកាក់ ស្នេហា និងចំណង់ចំណូលចិត្ត។ វានិយាយអំពីការ lobbying ការសងប្រាក់វិញ ការតភ្ជាប់ និងអំពើពុករលួយនៃសង្គមកូរ៉េតាមរយៈ Lee Cha Don ដែលបាត់បង់អ្វីៗគ្រប់យ៉ាងដោយសារតែលុយ។\n\nLee Cha Don គឺជាបុរសម្នាក់ដែលឡើងកាន់តំណែងជាព្រះរាជអាជ្ញាសាខាពិសេសជាមួយនឹងលុយរបស់អ្នកខ្ចីប្រាក់ ខណៈដែល Bok Jae In គឺជាកូនស្រីរបស់អ្នកខ្ចីប្រាក់ដែលបានចិញ្ចឹម Lee Cha Don។"},"poster":"https://i.ebayimg.com/00/s/MTYwMFgxMzE5/z/-xsAAOSwKFxjY4vP/$_57.JPG?set_id=880000500F","year":2013,"rating":7.8,"genres":["ACTION","COMEDY","ROMANCE","THRILLER","DRAMA"],"language":"English","episodeCount":17,"episodes":[{"ep":"1","title":{"en":"Episode 1","km":"ភាគទី1"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ipro855/am/refs/heads/n1/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"2","title":{"en":"Episode 2","km":"ភាគទី2"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ipro855/am/refs/heads/n2/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"3","title":{"en":"Episode 3","km":"ភាគទី3"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ipro855/am/refs/heads/n3/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"4","title":{"en":"Episode 4","km":"ភាគទី4"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ipro855/am/refs/heads/n4/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"5","title":{"en":"Episode 5","km":"ភាគទី5"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ipro855/am/refs/heads/n5/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"6","title":{"en":"Episode 6","km":"ភាគទី6"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ipro8